room_title: Escape room "The Jungle" by Escape Room Buffalo in Buffalo
review: Wonderful escape room! Such a great experience! Decor and clues really fitting, amazing and original! The owner was super great and friendly, and happy to answer any questions at the end! Absolutely going to come again and recommend to friends!

review: So much fun!! We've now completed each of the four rooms! The Jungle, the Brewery 2, Prison Break 2.0, and the Space Program. lots of details, great puzzles, can't wait for more!!!
